name: Arsenal
summary: In Premier League action, Arsenal staged a dramatic late comeback to defeat Leicester City 4-2, with stoppage-time goals securing the victory. Meanwhile, Manchester City had to settle for a 2-2 draw with 10-man Arsenal, with John Stones scoring a late equalizer. Also noteworthy, previews of the upcoming matches between Arsenal and Bayern Munich in the Women's Champions League and Arsenal and Hacken in the pre-season Emirates Cup were released. Additionally, a tribute was paid to former Arsenal player Fabian Caballero, who passed away at the age of 46.

name: Newcastle
summary: Newcastle United played two matches, one in the Premier League against Manchester City and another in the Premiership against Harlequins. In the Premier League, Newcastle United drew 1-1 with Manchester City, with Gordon scoring a penalty for Newcastle. In the Premiership, Harlequins defeated Newcastle Falcons 28-14, securing their first win of the season. Ticket information for Newcastle United's upcoming match against Arsenal is available on Arsenal.com. Live coverage and updates of the Newcastle v Manchester City match are available on The Guardian, BBC.com, and Al Jazeera English. Team news, kick-off time, and TV information for the Newcastle v Manchester City match can be found on Manchester City FC's website. The Harlequins squad that will host Newcastle is announced on quins.co.uk. Live scores and highlights for the Newcastle United vs Manchester City match are available on TNT Sports.
